        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>College Savings Recovery Act</strong></p> <p>This bill sets forth a special tax rule allowing a rollover to a Roth Individual Retirement Account (Roth IRA) from a long-term qualified tuition program (i.e., a 529 qualified tuition program) without penalty.</p>]]>
        </text>
